00:24:02,063 --> 00:24:11,945
Although there were conflicts, the building code appeals board in short determined that the design was proper and that it was allowed to be constructed in that manner.

237
00:24:12,545 --> 00:24:16,867
That building is currently under construction at 305 Winter Street in Waltham.

238
00:24:16,887 --> 00:24:26,549
