573
00:55:50,539 --> 00:55:51,799
It's the subsidizing agency.

574
00:55:52,620 --> 00:55:53,920
So during final approval,

575
00:55:54,700 --> 00:56:04,185
you know, when things are being nailed down before, you know, as part of the whole regulatory agreement and so forth, the developer's gonna have to show the subsidizing agency, here's where I wanna put my affordable units.

576
00:56:04,245 --> 00:56:07,426
And the subsidizing agencies are gonna approve it or they're gonna push back.

577
00:56:08,287 --> 00:56:11,188
And I've had experience of subsidizing agency pushing back.

578
00:56:11,248 --> 00:56:17,952
So I think people should just understand the interest in fair housing is not just at the local level, it's certainly at the state level as well.

